docs {
  # Get Date Range
  
  Returns the minimum and maximum transaction dates.
  
  ## Response
  
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "data": {
      "minDate": "2023-01-15",
      "maxDate": "2024-12-28"
    }
  }
  ```
}
